{"tid":1924591,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"確診阿迪達：身體好多了","createTime":"2020-03-13T18:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T00:55:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d393e2b3d417457f901a71444e6cde5b68740c7","tid":1924591,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:38:59.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】阿仙奴領隊阿迪達感染新型冠狀病毒後，周五首度開腔，表示身體情況已經好轉不少。<br />\n<br />\n「多謝大家的支持，我已經好多了。我們正面對巨大及前所未有的挑戰。現在所有人的健康才是最重要的事，大家要跟隨指引保護身邊所有人，我們一起捱過這個難關。」阿迪達（Mikel Arteta）在Twitter報平安。<br />\n<br />\n在這名37歲少帥確診後，阿仙奴關閉了訓練場，所有最近曾跟他接觸的員工都需要隔離，據知包括所有一隊的球員。阿仙奴總監雲卡迪深表示：「球會中人及大眾的健康是我們最關心的事。」<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭足總在周五宣佈，包括英超在內的所有足球比賽都暫停至4月3日。阿迪達十分同意這個做法，表示：「做得好！英超賽事作出了正確的決定。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"7c53b8e2bb63e977c5f26dfaab11550e7e985e7d","tid":1924591,"uid":191453,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:43:52.000Z","msg":"佢識講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fake news?"},{"pid":"d65be3278c7aadf0d5891aacd89d4031cc62bb35","tid":1924591,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c53b8e2bb63e977c5f26dfaab11550e7e985e7d","tid":1924591,"uid":191453,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:43:52.000Z","msg":"佢識講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fake news?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T00:51:52.000Z","msg":"確診阿迪達：身體好多了<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】阿仙奴領隊阿迪達感...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=28829996170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D28829996170&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=4e323aee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=28829996170</a><br />\n<br />\nNow 體育 - <a href=\"http://sports.now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu